structure.unit: ACQUISITION AND DEVELOPMENT OF PUBLIC PROJECTS THROUGH REVENUE BONDS

law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 375, sec. 11, effective July 15, 1998; amended ch. 69, sec. 22, effective July 15, 1998. -- Created 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 213, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1996.

metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/98). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 375 prevails over its amendment in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 69.
